OL,3,CUnmarked police vans deployed in
OL,4,Cspeeding crack down
OL,6,FUnmarked police vans are being
OL,7,Fdeployed in targeted locations across
OL,8,FBristol and Somerset in a bid to stop
OL,9,Fpersistent speeding.
OL,11,FAvon and Somerset Police said it has
OL,12,Fidentified specific areas of concern
OL,13,Fusing community reports, Speedwatch
OL,14,Fschemes and collision data.
OL,16,FThe scheme aims to deter speeding and
OL,17,Fprevent serious collisions by
OL,18,Fencouraging "consistent safe driving
OL,19,Fbehaviours," it said.
