OL,6,FPolice said there have been 43 deaths
OL,7,Fon roads in the Avon and Somerset area
OL,8,Fso far this year.
OL,10,FHead of roads policing and road
OL,11,Fsafety, Chief Inspector Robert
OL,12,FCheeseman, said: "The use of unmarked
OL,13,Fspeed detection vans is not about
OL,14,Fcatching people out - it's about
OL,15,Fprotecting lives."
