OL,3,CUnmarked police vans deployed in
OL,4,Cspeeding crack down
OL,6,FThe road safety enforcement vans are
OL,7,Fequipped with 360-degree cameras and
OL,8,Flong-range detection technology that
OL,9,Fcan also identify other road traffic
OL,10,Foffences, including failing to wear a
OL,11,Fseatbelt and using a handheld device
OL,12,Fwhile driving.
OL,14,FInfrared cameras on the vans mean that
OL,15,Fpolice operations can also be carried
OL,16,Fout at night.
