OL,3,CUnmarked police vans deployed in
OL,4,Cspeeding crack down
OL,6,FMr Cheeseman added: "Speeding is one
OL,7,Fof the leading causes of fatal and
OL,8,Fserious injury collisions, and we are
OL,9,Fcommitted to using every tool at our
OL,10,Fdisposal to address this.
OL,12,F"The introduction of unmarked road
OL,13,Fsafety enforcement vans represents a
OL,14,Fsignificant step forward in our
OL,15,Fcommitment to reducing road fatalities
OL,16,Fand serious injuries.
OL,18,F"We urge all motorists to adhere to
OL,19,Fspeed limits and recognise that road
OL,20,Fsafety is a collective responsibility".
